Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.29,0:03:20.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.91,0:03:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have come to Dressrosa\Nto hand Caesar over to Doflamingo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When Luffy found out that the \Nprize for a fighting event
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,was the Flare-Flare Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.27,0:03:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he decided to enter and fight fierce \Nbattles against other tough
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.43,0:03:53.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,contenders from the New World.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come after me, Doflamingo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Is he gonna go across the bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Doflamingo!\NThey have nothing to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doflamingo is flying towards us!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! A nightmare?!\NAre we gonna get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch this, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll viciously slay your allies\Nright before your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy, help...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends are crying in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.27,0:05:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes quite a tough one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.18,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Big Clash!\NSanji vs. Doflamingo!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the "Black Foot" of \Nthe Straw Hats, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Premiere Hachis Hash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pentachromatic Strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0}!\N--What did Doflamingo do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save your friends if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doflamingo is coming this way!\N--You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stay away from us!\N--Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.25,0:06:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Diable Jambe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Poele a Frire...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spectre!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's powerful! He's quite strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What happened? I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Sanji-{\i1}san{\i0} got frozen in mid air!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been grappled\Nby the Young Master's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo's power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot is like a bug caught\Nin a spider's web now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he can do is wait for death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is it?!\N--A whip?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything! Just run!\NUse Coup de Burst to get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Overheat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:11.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.71,0:08:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tra-guy! He saved Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I made a mistake!\NLet's get on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I'm on the ship again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.37,0:08:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Giolla! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being held captive, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I dropped my guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Doflamingo's coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Foot-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.61,0:09:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the plan to destroy\Nthe factory going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found out where it is
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Franky said it's gonna \Nbe harder than we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's my father?! And Kanjuro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NSan-goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are they doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momonosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai is heading to the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be alright once everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we need more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!\NIs that my heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you keeping it in the cabin?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had your heart with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You had it in your body the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.20,0:10:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to take him\Nand head for Zou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.21,0:10:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.64,0:10:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you the Vivre Card\Nthat leads you to the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a Vivre Card?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It'll point toward an island called Zou\Nthat I talked about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.46,0:10:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head for the island?!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Luffy-{\i1}san{\i0} and the others?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing left to do on this island is\Ndestroy the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.87,0:10:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll catch up with you guys soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! We'll wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.77,0:11:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't set sail without our captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.22,0:11:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy ship is flying towards us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.15,0:11:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is that possible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.48,0:11:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It must be Fujitora.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo is coming from that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy ship is getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.29,0:11:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can wait here if you want\Nbut don't let them take Caesar!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.43,0:12:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.39,0:12:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's falling from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.39,0:12:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteorites?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy-{\i1}kun{\i0}, we "Spiral Hats" are\Ngonna leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.30,0:12:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.63,0:12:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realize we have\Nto carry Caesar as far as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.17,0:12:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear we have to leave here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.98,0:12:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought Dressrosa was just a waypoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our main purpose was killing Kaido \Nof the Four Emperors, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.79,0:12:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you getting too hung up\Non Doflamingo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteorites! Meteorites!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho-{\i1}san{\i0}, they hit the bottom of our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I hadn't thought about that.\NLaw-{\i1}san{\i0} is there, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop eating?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.54,0:13:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get back to Dressrosa now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.21,0:13:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the war...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will turn, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell them to turn around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.08,0:14:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whip, again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.52,0:14:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excess Whip String!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.30,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-{\i1}ya{\i0}! Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to sail where there are no clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo is a String-String Fruit eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.41,0:15:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He moves through the air\Nby attaching strings to clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't follow you if there are no clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strings? I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready for Coup de Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, what do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.04,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}, don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you!\NI want to ask you something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you on the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:16:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to you! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can't you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.91,0:16:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just met my hero - Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} today
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now, Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0} is talking to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.93,0:16:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop crying from happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.73,0:16:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI wonder who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I don't know who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut can you tell us how to enter the Colosseum?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.39,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the doors are closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0} is asking me a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.89,0:16:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad that I sailed out to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.53,0:16:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like he got very excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.76,0:17:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, calm down and listen. We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.37,0:17:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you were there to see it, Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-{\i1}senpai{\i0} was awesome as hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard him say Luffy-{\i1}dono{\i0}\Nand Zoro-{\i1}dono{\i0}'s names now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he know who you two are?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the battle royal here\Nin the Corrida Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one winner from Block D can\Nmove to the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are all fighting intensely\Nto get that one spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.19,0:18:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The way she moves...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NI don't think she's just another gladiator.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why doesn't she make an \Nattack even passing up
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:13.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,some critical chances?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.36,0:18:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is she doing?!\NShe's at the edge of the ring!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better worry about yourself\Nbefore you worry about someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rebecca will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.57,0:18:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop backing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're at the edge now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.22,0:19:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Stay at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare for death, you little tramp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.16,0:19:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just finish her off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my girl, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.39,0:20:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we barely outran\Nthe Navy and Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna head for Zou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? No, wait, Sanji!\NAre you gonna leave us?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get through somehow and meet us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm ready to get away\Nas soon as I have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.19,0:20:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.92,0:20:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, we'll be alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.73,0:20:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go to Zou (elephant)\Nor Giraffe or wherever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna destroy the factory for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.87,0:20:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are Luffy and Law doing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro and Kin'emon went\Nto tell Luffy what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:22:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in letting half \Nof the Straw Hats get away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other half is in Dressrosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I take them as hostages,\Nthey'll come back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right away to return Caesar to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.78,0:22:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that you knew\Nthere are quite a few people...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who underestimated them like that\Nand got burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that I have to break up my alliance\Nwith the Straw Hats now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I joined forces with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my only purpose was to use them\Nto stop the manufacture of SMILEs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't kill you right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.33,0:22:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaido will kill you sooner or later\Nonce you lose all the SMILEs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.06,0:23:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna sacrifice \Nyourself to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.46,0:23:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see how the world \Nfalls into a mess after you die,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but more importantly, I want to make \Nyou pay for what you did 13 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:18.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,
